<p><strong>User experience:</strong> Potential customers reading reviews see that you care about feedback. This increases click-through rates, which feeds behavioral signals.</p>
<p><strong>E-E-A-T signals:</strong> Responding demonstrates expertise and trustworthiness. Google evaluates these qualities across your entire digital presence.</p>
